casebody.data:
Thursday, April 2, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

97-1173. Keefe v. Youngstown Diocese of the Catholic Church.

Stark App. No. 1996CA00265. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Stark County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to participate in oral argument currently scheduled for May 12,1998,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to participate in oral argument be, and hereby is, denied.
